## Layer Rules

DDP — see `flutter-architecture` skill for the full table.

Quick reference:
- Domain → pure Dart, no Flutter, no Riverpod, no I/O
- Data → implements Domain abstractions, uses helpers
- Presentation → consumes Domain via Riverpod providers + usecases

